{"tid":1217222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實如果逃犯條例通過 英國或會成為最大贏家","createTime":"2019-06-13T12:23:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:34:21.000Z","uid":181044,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9580698b482b0414706b4c8cc0f95f613f2a77a9","tid":1217222,"uid":181044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:23:39.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得當年 中英簽左 50年不變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果逃犯條例真係通過 姐係代表中國並無守到當年簽下條約 咁如果計番上黎 姐係中國違約 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咁香港或者可以由英國黎接管番<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時件事就會愈搞愈大 最後可能<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">彭定康再接管不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n所以其實件事點發展 今次就咁睇都好似幾難輸 同埋阿爺都好醒 即刻出新聞話呢件事唔關佢地事 係慈母自行要咁做<br />\n<br />\n不過都係個句 支持到既支持 話哂都係大家既屋企<br />\n<br />\n雖然班克警 係被人拍底好多證據 不合當使用武力 但係大家要記得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最緊要係條例行先</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 第一次開po就因為呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f7639cbc6566b91bcd58256ab4e3e2415949c1","tid":1217222,"uid":181044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}